{"tid":1876933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020DSE打氣區 辛苦曬考生手足","createTime":"2020-02-12T17:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T20:32:19.000Z","uid":210495,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c576e84f2d00fbd2e94219ea7b8f52e108f8b4c","tid":1876933,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"呢個學年大家都辛苦啦<br />\n由其是係中六準備考2020dse嘅手足<br />\n2019就要抗爭 2020就要驚肺炎<br />\n當中有大埔比狗打到ptsd要defer嘅<br />\n保釋唔到有機會考唔到試嘅<br />\n同屋企嘈咗幾個月嘅<br />\n因為抗爭而要追讀書schedule嘅<br />\n同埋擔心緊到底會唔會延期考 oral會唔會取消<br />\n仲有好多好多手足<br />\n<br />\n想係呢度同各位2020DSE手足講聲加油<br />\n呢排就溫住書先<br />\n有咩心聲都可以當呢個post係樹窿<br />\n不論延期到幾時 你地都要爭曬所有學位<br />\n大學等緊你地！！！<br />\n<br />\n留名同2020考生手足打個氣"},{"pid":"b1c99e2014ca414b4ce7ea1c77fd91b6fb4b1975","tid":1876933,"uid":234120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T18:02:46.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855f43e91215d862876f15b86c4a5bb7ffcfc86d","tid":1876933,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T20:32:19.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}